Additional Imagery:
Brain MRI courtesy Dr Bruno Di Munzio: https://radiopaedia.org/cases/normal-brain-mri-4

Descartes. Diagram of the brain and nerves by Wellcome

Brain and Spinal Cord Illustration by Wellcome

These cases are patients who I, or my colleagues have seen. They are de-identified and many instances have been presented in more depth in an academic setting. These videos are not individual medical advice and are for general educational purposes only.  I do not give medical advice over the internet, see your own physician in person for that.

This video was recorded with a Canon C200, Sony A7R3, and iPhone 11 Pro. All writing, narration, editing, and animations are by the presenter.

References: 

[0] Choudhry SA. et. al. Cureus. 2017 Sep; 9(9): e1666. 

[1] Baumert M, Maycox PR, Navone F, De Camilli P, Jahn R. EMBO J. 1989 Feb; 8(2): 379–384. 

[2] Ciottone GR. Toxidrome Recognition. N Engl J Med 2018; 378:1611-1620.

[3] Clin Infect Dis. 2018 Jan 15; 66(Suppl 1): S43–S56. 

[4] Schantz EJ. et. al. Microbiol Rev. 1992 Mar;56(1):80-99. 1579114

[5] Blasi, J. et. al. Nature, 1993, Vol.365(6442), p.160

[6] Drachman DB. et. al. N Engl J Med. 1982 Sep 23;307(13):769-75.

[7] Conti-Fine BM. et. al. J Clin Invest. 2006 Nov;116(11):2843-54.

Please see the great PDF by Lewis S Nelson and Lauren K Shawn published in 2012 on this topic.

snippet.title: SPIDERMAN Return Explained! Avengers Future & Feige's Master Plan!
snippet.description:
Spider-Man is back in the MCU thanks to a new deal signed by Disney and Sony... but what really happened here? Was this whole Spider-Man MCU breakup STAGED to set up the far future of Spider-Man and the Marvel Cinematic Universe over the next five years? Erik Voss explains the narrative implications of Spider-Man 3 and the Marvel mystery movie that Spider-Man will appear in thanks to this deal. Will Spider-Man introduce the Fantastic Four to the MCU? Mutants like Ice Man and Firestar? Street-level heroes like Daredevil, Blade, and She-Hulk? Or pass the torch to new young characters like Richard Rider NOVA?

snippet.title: Why US Airports Are So Bad
snippet.description:
U.S. airports, for the most part, are publicly owned and operated by either a city, a county, a state or in some cases, a public authority. But, in the face of decaying infrastructure, a handful of U.S. airports have started to abandon the public model and turned to private money to fund billion dollar projects. In 2016, New York State and the Port Authority partnered with Delta Airlines and LaGuardia Gateway Partners to completely rebuild the airport. LaGuardia airport is now getting an $8 billion overhaul.

snippet.title: Frozen 2 | "Into The Unknown" Special Look
snippet.description:
Check out a new look at Disney’s Frozen 2, featuring the brand-new song “Into The Unknown.” See Frozen 2 in theaters November 22. 

Why was Elsa born with magical powers? What truths about the past await Elsa as she ventures into the unknown to the enchanted forests and dark seas beyond Arendelle? The answers are calling her but also threatening her kingdom. Together with Anna, Kristoff, Olaf and Sven, she'll face a dangerous but remarkable journey. In “Frozen,” Elsa feared her powers were too much for the world. In “Frozen 2,” she must hope they are enough. From the Academy Award®-winning team—directors Jennifer Lee and Chris Buck, producer Peter Del Vecho and songwriters Kristen Anderson-Lopez and Robert Lopez—and featuring the voices of Idina Menzel, Kristen Bell, Jonathan Groff and Josh Gad, Walt Disney Animation Studios’ “Frozen 2” opens in U.S. theaters on Nov. 22, 2019.

Facebook: https://facebook.com/DisneyFrozen/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DisneyFrozen

snippet.title: LUNAR BEAUTY SPOOKY HOLIDAY REVEAL! MOON SPELL COLLECTION
snippet.description:

WE ARE FINALLY HERE WITH THE LUNAR BEAUTY HOLIDAY 2019 COLLECTION REVEAL! You guys I have been working on this for SO long.. Moon Spell means so much to me and my childhood and I hope you guys can see the love and energy I put into this entire collection! WE DID THAT YALL!

The Moon Spell Collection will be available this friday on October 4th at 10 AM PST on Lunarbeauty.com :D there will be amazing deals and bundles for those asking! Also this collection is limited edition so if you want it…. baby you better get her! We wanted a gorgeous capsule collection and thats exactly what we got! WOO! 
Hope you love it as much as I do! Just 5 more days! 

LUNAR BEAUTY CONTEST!

snippet.title: Everybody's Everything Official Trailer (2019) | Lil Peep Documentary | In Theaters Nov 2019
snippet.description:
Everybody's Everything - The Official Lil Peep Feature Length Documentary | In Theaters November 2019

Visit http://www.EverybodyseverythingMovie.com for tickets and info.

Creating a unique mix of punk, emo and trap, Lil Peep was set to bring a new musical genre to the mainstream when he died of a drug overdose at just 21 years old. From the streets of Los Angeles to studios in London and sold out tours in Russia, the artist born Gustav Ahr touched countless lives through his words, his sound and his very being.

Executive produced by Terrence Malick, Everybody’s Everything is an intimate, humanistic portrait that seeks to understand an artist who attempted to be all things to all people.

DIRECTORS
Sebastian Jones & Ramez Silyan  

PRODUCER
Ben Soley  

EXECUTIVE
PRODUCERS
Terrence Malick, Liza Womack, and Sarah Stennett

snippet.title: The Gun Detector - Smarter Every Day 225
snippet.description:
We built a gun detector using machine learning that works with existing surveillance cameras. 
Get started with 8 free meals – that’s $80 off your first month of HelloFresh. Go to https://bit.ly/2PGu55r and enter smarter80
Click here if you're interested in subscribing: http://bit.ly/Subscribe2SED
⇊  Click below for more links!  ⇊
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GET SMARTER SECTION

There are many companies working on this type of technology at the moment.  We made ours in 2018, and Chad visited my house in January 2019 to film most of this.  We didn't post it for various reasons, but decided now might be a good time.  The fidelity of the inference is a function of how you train it.... so obviously the more data points you provide, the better it will perform.  This particular type of machine learning is known as object detection, with the computation being performed by a deep neural network "on the edge".  The video stream is processed locally and no internet is needed to find the object in real time. If you're working on something similar or could use this technology in your systems and would like to collaborate....
